hadiths[143]{hadithnumber,text}:
4351,Janab Ikrima se riwayat hai ke Saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne baaz logon ko jo deen Islam se murtad ho gaey they aag se jalwa diya. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko ye khabar pahunchi to unhoney kaha ke main unhen aag se na jalwaata . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''Allah ke azab se azab mat do .'' mein unhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke farman ke mutabiq qatl karta. bila-shuba Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''jo apna deen badal ley usey qatl kar do .'' Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye baat pahunchi to unhoney kaha : kya khoob hain ibne-Abbas ! (ya ibne-Abbas ki maa ! ( .
4352,"Saiyedna Abdullah (bin Masood ( (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo musalman is baat ki gawahi deta hai ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud nahin aur main Allah ka Rasool hun, uska khoon halal nahin hai, siwaye uskey ke teen baaton mein se kisi eik ka murtakib ho. shaadi shuda ho kar zina karey, jaan ke badley jaan aur jo deen ( Islam ( chhod dey aur jamaat ( millat Islam ( se alag ho jaey.''"
4353,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo musalman gawahi deta ho ke Allah ke siwa aur koi mabud nahin aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ke Rasool hain uska khoon halal nahin, siwaye uskey ke teen baaton mein se kisi eik ka murtakib ho : shaadi shuda honey ke baad zina karey, to usey patharon se rajm kya jaeyga , koi Allah aur uskey Rasool ke khilaf hathiyar utha kar nikley to usey qatl kya jaeyga ya sooli chadhaya jaeyga ya mulk Badr kar diya jaey ya koi kisi jaan ko maar daley to usey uskey badley mein qatl kya jaeyga.''"
4354,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua jabke merey sath bano Ash'ar ke do aadmi aur bhi they, eik meri daain janib tha aur doosra baain janib . un dono ne kaam ( kisi mansab aur zimme daari (ka sawal kar diya aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khamosh rahey . phir aapney farmaya : ''aey Abu-Musa ! '' ya farmaya : ''aey Abdullah bin Qais ! tera kya khayal hai? ''maine arz kya : qasam us zaat ki jisney aap ko haq ke sath bheja hai ! unhoney mujhey apney dil ki baat nahin batai thi aur mujhey khayal na tha ke ye kisi mansab ke talabgar hain, aur goya main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki miswak ki taraf dekh raha hun jo aap ke hont ke nichey thi jis se wo ooper ko uth sa gaya tha. aapney farmaya : '' ham kisi ko apna kaam hergiz na sonpengey .'' ya farmaya : '' ham aisey kisi shakhs ko apna kaam nahin detey hain jo khud se uska talabgar ho, lekin aey Abu-Musa ! '' ya farmaya ''aey Abdullah bin Qais ! tum jao .'' aur unhen Yamen ki taraf bhej diya. phir unke peechey Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi bhej diya. jab Muaz unke paas pahunchey to Abu-Musa ne kaha : tashrif laaiye . utariye aur unhen takiya pesh kya. lekin Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne achcha dekha ke unke yahan eik aadmi zanjeeron mein jakda hua tha. unhoney poochha, usey kya hai? kaha ke ye yahudi tha, phir musalman ho gaya lekin dobara apney batil deen ki taraf phir gaya (murtad ho gaya) hai. Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : jab tak usey qatl na kar diya jaey mein nahin bethunga, ye faisla hai Allah aur uskey Rasool ka , Abu-Musa ne kaha beth jaiye, haan, (faisla yehi hai.) Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : jab tak usey qatl na kar diya jaey mein nahin bethunga. ye faisla Allah aur uskey Rasool ka hai, unhoney teen baar kaha . chunanche Abu-Musa ne hukm diya aur usey qatl kar diya gaya. phir wo dono qiyamullail (raat ki Namaz (ke mutalliq baat cheet kartey rahey . un mein se eik , yani Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main sota hun aur qiyam bhi karta hun. ya kaha ke qiyam karta hun aur sota bhi hun aur apni neend mein usi chiz ka umeedwar hota hun jiski mujhey apney qiyam mein umeed hoti hai. (yani ajr w sawab ki .)"
4355,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main jab Yamen mein) aamil ( tha to Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) merey yahan tashrif laye aur eik aadmi tha jo yahudi tha, usney Islam qubul kya magar phir Islam se murtad ho gaya. jab Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laye to unhoney kaha : main apni sawari se us waqt tak nahin utrunga jab tak ke usey qatl na kar diya jaey. dono ( Talha aur Barida ( mein se eik ne kaha : aur us shakhs ko us se pehley tauba kar leney ka kaha gaya tha."
4356,"Janab abu-Barda ne ye qissa bayan kya, kehtey hain ke Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan eik aadmi pesh kya gaya jo Islam se murtad ho chuka tha. to aap usey taqreeban bees raat dawat detey rahey . phir Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif ley aaye to unhoney bhi usey dawat di magar usney inkar kar diya, to uski gardan maar di gaee . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke us riwayat ko Abdul-Malik bin Umair ne abu-Barda se riwayat kya hai magar us mein tauba karaney ka bayan nahin. aur ibne-fuzail ne b-waasta shebani, Saeed bin abi burda se unhoney apney walid Abu-Musa se riwayat kya to us mein bhi tauba karaney ka zikr nahin hai."
4357,Janab Qasim (bin Abdur-Rehman Hazli ( ne ye qissa bayan kya. us mein hai ke Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) apni sawari se us waqt tak na utrey jab tak ke uski gardan na maar di gaee aur us shakhs se tauba na karwaai.
4358,"Saiyedna ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Abdullah bin Saad bin Abu-Sarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka kaatib tha. to shetan ne usey behka liya aur wo kuffar se ja mila . phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Fateh Makka ke din uskey mutalliq hukm diya ke usey qatl kar diya jaey. to Hazrat Usman bin Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ne uskey liye aman talab kar li , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey aman de-di."
4359,"Hazrat Saad (bin abi Waqas ( (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab Fateh Makka ka din aaya to Abdullah bin Saad bin Abu-Sarah Saiyedna Usman bin Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan chup gaya , phir Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) usey ley aaye yahan tak ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney la khada kya aur darkhast ki : aey Allah ke Rasool ! Abdullah se baiat ley liijiye. aapney apna sar uthaya aur uski taraf dekha, teen baar aisey hua , aap her baar inkar farmatey rahey, teesri baar ke baad aapney us se baiat le-li. phir apney Sahaba ki taraf mutawajjeh huey aur farmaya : ''kya tum mein koi samajhdaar aadmi nahin tha ke jab maine uski baiat leney se apna haath rok rakha tha to wo uski taraf uthta aur usey qatl kar daalta ?'' Sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham nahin jantey they ke aap ke ji mein kya hai? aap hamen apni aankh se ishara farma detey . aapney farmaya : '' kisi Nabi ko laaiq nahin ke uski aankh khayanat wali ho.''"
4360,"Hazrat Jarir (bin Abdullah bijli ( (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''jab koi ghulam shirk ki taraf bhag jaey to uska khoon halal hai.''"
4361,"Saiyedna ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik na-bina tha, uski eik umme-walad ( aisi londi jis se uski aulad ( thi aur wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko gaaliyaan bakti aur bura bhala kehti thi. wo usey mana karta tha magar maanti na thi , wo usey daant-ta tha magar samajhti na thi. eik raat wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki badgoi kerney aur aap ko gaaliyaan deney lagi to us na-beena ne eik barchha liya, usey us londi ke pet par rakh kar us par apna bojh dal diya aur is tarah usey qatl kar dala . us londi ke paon main eik chhota bacha aa gaya aur usney us jagah ko khoon se lathpath kar diya. jab subh hui to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se us qatl ka zikr kya gaya aur log ikhattey ho gaey to aapney farmaya : ''main us aadmi ko Allah ki qasam deta hun, jisney ye karrawai ki hai aur mera us par haq hai ke khada ho jaey.'' to wo na-bina khada ho gaya aur logon ki gardanen phalaangtaa hua aaya, uskey qadam laraz rahey they yahan tak ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney aa betha aur bola : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main uska qatil hun. ye aap ko gaaliyaan bakti aur bura bhala kehti thi. main usko mana karta tha magar baaz na aati thi. main usey daant-ta tha magar samajhti na thi. merey us se do bachey bhi hain jaisey ke moti hon aur wo mera bada achcha sath deney wali thi. pichhli raat jab wo aap ko gaaliyaan deney lagi aur bura bhala kehney lagi to maine chhura liya , usey uskey pet par rakha aur us par apna bojh dal diya yahan tak ke usko qatl kar dala. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' khabrdar ! gawah ho jao us londi ka khoon zaya hai.''"
4362,Saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik yahudi aurat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko gaaliyaan diya karti thi aur aap ke baarey mein naazeba alfaz bolti thi. to eik aadmi ne uska gala ghoont diya yahan tak ke wo mar gaee . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uska khoon zaya qarar diya.
4363,"Hazrat abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main Saiyedna abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas tha ke wo kisi aadmi par naraz huey aur bahut ziyada naraz huey. maine kaha : aey khalifa Rasool! ijazat diijiye ke main uski gardan maar dalun? to meri is baat ne unka sab ghussa zaayel kar diya. phir wo wahan se uth kar ghar chaley gaey aur mujhey bulwa bheja aur kaha : tum ne abhi abhi kya kaha tha? maine arz kya ke maine kaha tha : mujhey ijazat den mein uski gardan maar dun . farmaya agar main tujhey aisey keh deta to kya waqae tum ye kar guzartey? maine kaha : haan . farmaya : nahin, Allah ki qasam ! Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baad kisi Bishr ko ye maqam hasil nahin. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : ye lafz Yazid bin Zaree ke hain. Imam Ahmed bin Hanbal (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : yani abu-Bakar ko koi haq nahin ke kisi ko qatl karey siwaye uskey ke teen mein se koi eik baat ho, jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaai hai : ''emaan ke baad kufr, shaadi shuda honey ke baad zina aur kisi jaan ko kisi jaan ke badley ke baghair qatl kar dalna aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko haq tha ke wo kisi ko qatl kar dalen ."
4364,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke qabeela Ukul ya Uraina ke kuch log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye . unhen Madiney ki aab w hua raas na aai (aur bimar ho gaey ( to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko chand oontniyaan inayat farmaeyn aur hukm diya ke wo unka peshab aur doodh piyen . chunanche wo ( bahir charaagah mein) chaley gaey. jab tandurust huey to unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke charwahey ko qatl kar dala aur janwer hanka ley gaey. din ke pehley pahar hi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko unki khabar mil gaee to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unke taaqqub mein apney aadmi bhejey . jab din khoob chadh aaya to unhen ley aaya gaya. aapney unke mutalliq hukm diya to unke haath aur paon kaat daley gaey. unki aakhon mein garm lohey ke salaakhein pheri gaeen aur pathreeli zameen par phenk diye gaey, wo pani maangtey they magar na diya gaya. abu-Qulaba ne kaha : un logon ne chori ki, qatl kiye, emaan laney ke baad kufr kya aur Allah aur uskey Rasool se jang ki. (yani unke sath us sakht tareen maamley ki wajeh unke yehi qusur they.)"
4365,"Janab Ayub (Rahimahullah) ne apni sanad se ye hadees bayan ki, us mein hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne salaakhon ka hukm diya, unhen garm kya gaya aur phir unke aakhon mein pher diya aur unke haath paon kaat daley aur unhen dagh na diya (ke khoon hi band ho jaey aur unhen yakdam qatl na kya gaya .)"
4366,"Janab abu-Qulaba ne Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se ye hadees riwayat ki hai, us mein hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unke taaqqub mein mukhbiron ( khojiyon ( ko bheja to unhen ley aaya gaya , chunanche Allah taala ne usi silsiley mein ye aayat mubaarka nazil farmaai ( { إِنَّمَا جَزَاءُ الَّذِينَ يُحَارِبُونَ اللَّهَ وَرَسُولَهُ . . . } ( ''jo log Allah aur uskey Rasool se laden aur zameen mein fasad phailaaein (unki saza ye hai ke unhen qatl kar diya jaey ya sooli chadha diye jaeyn ya ulti atraaf se unke haath paon kaat diye jaeyn ya unhen jilaa watan kar diya jaey.'' ("
4367,"Janab Sabit , Qatada aur Humaid ne Saiyedna Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se ye hadees riwayat ki, kaha : ulti taraf se unke haath aur paon kaatey .) hadees ke) shuru mein kaha : wo oonton ko haank ley gaey aur Islam se murtad ho gaey . Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain : maine un mein se eik ko dekha ke wo piyas ke maarey apney munh se zameen ko kaat raha tha yahan tak ke wo ( usi haalat mein) mar gaey ."
4368,"Janab Qatada ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se ye hadees mazkura baala ki manind riwayat ki aur mazeed kaha : phir musla se mana kar diya gaya. aur us riwayat mein '' ulti atraaf sey, ka zikr nahin kya.  Shoba ne b-waasta Qatada aur salam bin miskeen , Sabit se aur usney Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya. un dono ne bhi '' ulti atraaf '' ka zikr nahin kya. aur Hammad bin Salma ki riwayat ke ilawa mujhey kisi ki hadees mein ye nahin mila ke aapney unke haath aur paon ulti taraf se kaatey they."
4369,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke kuch logon ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke oonton par daaka dala aur unhen haank ley gaey, Islam se murtad ho gaey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke charwahey ko qatl kya jo sahibe-emaan tha. to aapney unka taaqqub karwaya aur unhen pakad liya gaya. phir aapney unke haath aur paon kaatey aur unki aakhon mein garm salaakhein pherin, kaha ke un hi logon ke maamley mein aayate-muhaarba utri ( { إِنَّمَا جَزَاءُ الَّذِينَ يُحَارِبُونَ اللَّهَ وَرَسُولَهُ . . . } الخ (aur yehi wo log they jinkey baarey mein Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hajjaj bin Yusuf ko bataya tha jabke usney un se ye puchha tha."
4370,Janab abu-Zanaad se riwayat hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne oontniyaan chori kerney walon ke haath paon kaatey aur unki aankhon mein garm salaakhein pherein tu Allah taala ne aap ko us par itaab farmaya aur ye aayat nazil ki) { إِنَّمَا جَزَاءُ الَّذِينَ يُحَارِبُونَ اللَّهَ وَرَسُولَهُ . . . . } ( الخ ( al-Maaida : 33 (
4371,"Imam Muhammad bin Sirin kehtey hain ke ye amal ehkame-hudood nazil honey se pehley ka hai, yani jo hadees Anas mein mazkur hua hai."
4372,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke (Sura Al-Maaida ki aayat : 33 ,34) ({ إِنَّمَا جَزَاءُ الَّذِينَ يُحَارِبُونَ اللَّهَ وَرَسُولَهُ . . . }) ''un logon ki saza jo Allah taala se aur uskey Rasool se laden aur zameen mein fasad kartey phiren yehi hai ke wo qatl kar diye jaeyn, ya sooli chadha diye jaeyn ya ultey taur se unke haath paon kaat diye jaeyn ya unhen jilaa watan kar diya jaey, ye to hui unki duniyaawi zillat aur khawari aur aakhirat mein unke liye bada bhari azab hai. haan jo log is se pehley tauba kar lein ke tum un par ikhtiyar pa lo to yaqeen mano ke Allah taala bahut badi bakhshish aur rehem aur karam wala hai.'' ye aayat mushrekin ke baarey mein nazil hui hai. to jo un mein se qabu paey janey se pehley tauba kar ley ye aayat uskey haq mein is baat ki maane (rukawat) nahin hai ke jo jurm usney kiya hai uski saza us par laagoo na ho."
4373,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Quraish ko bano makhzoom ki us aurat ki bahut fikr hui jisney chori ki thi. unhoney kaha ke is silsiley mein kon baat kar sakta hai? yani Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se. kehney lagey ke Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ke alawa aur koi ye jur'at nahin kar sakta , wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke chahetey hain. chunanche Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap se baat ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Usama ! kya us had mein sifarish kartey ho jo Allah ki hudood mein se hai?'' phir aap khadey huey aur khutba diya, aur farmaya : ''tum se pehley log sirf isi wajeh se halak huey they ke un mein jab koi moazziz aadmi chori kar leta to wo usey chhod detey, aur agar koi kamzor chori karta to us par had qaaim kar detey they. aur Allah ki qasam ! agar Muhammad ki beti Fatima bhi chori karti to main uska bhi haath kaat daalta.''"
4374,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke bano makhzoom ki eik aurat thi jo chizen mang kar ley jati aur phir un se mukar jati thi. chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uska haath kaatney ka hukm diya aur mazkura baala hadees Leis ke manind qissa bayan kiya. kaha : chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uska haath kaat dala. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ibne-Wahab ne ye hadees b-waaste Yunus , Zohri se riwayat ki aur usi tarah kaha jaisey ke Leis ne bayan kiya ke eik aurat ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein Fateh Makka ke dino mein chori kar li. aur Leis ne ba-waaste Yunus, ibne-Shahab se apni sanad se riwayat kiya to kaha : eik aurat koi chiz mang kar ley gaee . Masood bin Aswad ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se is hadees ki manind riwayat kiya, kaha : us aurat ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ghar se eik chadar chori ki. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : aur Abu-Zubair ne Saiyedna Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya ke eik aurat ne chori kar li phir Sayeda Zenab dukhtar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan ja kar panah ley-li. aur Sufiyan bin Uena ne isey ba-waaste Ayub bin Musa, an (an) Zohri , an (an) Urwa , an (an) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) riwayat kiya. aur Sufiyan se riwayat kerney walon mein alfaz riwayat ka ikhtilaf hai, un mein se baaz kehtey hain ke wo aurat chizen mang kar ley jati thi aur baaz kehtey hain ke wo chori karti thi , aur Shuaib Zohri ke wastey an (an) Urwa an (an) Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan kartey hain to kehtey hain ke wo aurat chizen mang kar ley jati thi aur aagey mazkura hadees bayan ki. aur jab Ismail bin Umayya aur Is-haq bin Rashid dono Zohri se bayan kartey hain to kehtey hain ke us aurat ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ghar se chori ki thi aur baqi hadees mazkura hadees ki misl (jaisi) bayan ki."
4375,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''izzat daar logon ki khtaen maaf kar diya karo siwaye iskey ke sharae hudood hon.''
4376,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''hudood ke maamlat ko aapas hi main eik doosrey ko maaf kar diya karo lekin jo haq ka muqadma mujh tak pahunch gaya to phir usko zaroor laagu kiya jaeyga."
4377,Yazid bin Nueim apney walid (Naeem bin Hazaal Aslami (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain ke Maaiz bin Malik Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya aur aap ke samney chaar baar aetraaf aur iqrar kiya (ke usney zina kiya hai) to aapney usko rajm (sangsaar) karney ka hukm diya aur Hazaal Aslami se farmaya : ''agar to is par apney kapdey se parda dal deta to terey liye behtar hota.''
4378,Janab ibne Mankadr (Rahimahullah) se riwayat hai ke Hazaal (Raziallahu anhu) ne Maaiz se kaha ke wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas jaey aur apney maamley ki khabar dey.
4379,"Janab Alqama bin Waael apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney main eik aurat Namaz ke iraday se nikli , to raastey mein usey eik mard mila jo us par chadh baitha aur us se apni nafsani khahish puri ki, wo cheekhi chillhaee aur wo chala gaya. phir aurat ke paas se eik aur aadmi guzra to wo boli ke yehi wo hai jisney merey sath aisey aisey kiya hai. muhajrin ki eik jamaat wahan se guzri to aurat ne kaha : beshak us aadmi ne merey sath aisey aisey kiya hai. to wo gaey aur usey pakad laye jiskey baarey mein usney guman kiya ke isney uskey sath mubashrat ki hai. wo usey pakad kar aurat ke paas laye to usney kaha : haan yehi wo hai. isliye wo usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas ley aaye . jab aapney uskey mutalliq hukm diya (yani had laganey ka ( to asal mujrim jo aurat ke sath mulawwis hua tha khada ho gaya aur bola : aey Allah ke Rasool ! uska mujrim mein hun. aapney us aurat se farmaya : ''tum jao, Allah ne tumhen maaf kar diya hai.'' aur us aadmi ke mutalliq achhey kalimaat farmaey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : yani us aadmi ke mutalliq jo (shubhe mein) pakda gaya tha. aur jo murtakib hua tha uskey mutalliq farmaya ke ''usey rajm (sangsar) kar do.'' phir farmaya : ''usney aisi tauba ki hai agar ye (tauba) ehale-Madina kartey to bhi qubul kar li jati. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is riwayat ko Asbaat bin Nasar ne bhi Simaak se riwayat kiya hai."
4380,"Hazrat Abu-Umaiya Makhzoomi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas eik chor ko laya gaya jisney khud se aetraaf kiya magar maal uskey paas se nahin mila tha. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se kaha : ''main nahin samajhta ke to ne chori ki hogi.'' usney kaha : kyon nahin (yani ki hai). Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do ya teen baar aisey hi kaha. phir aapney hukm diya to uska haath kaat dala gaya. phir pesh kiya gaya to aapney us se farmaya : ''Allah se maafi maango aur tauba karo.'' usney kaha : main Allah se maafi maangta hun aur tauba karta hun. aapney farmaya : ''aey Allah ! iski tauba qubul farma ley.''  teen baar farmaya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : is riwayat ko Amr bin Aasim ne ba-waaste Hammam , Is'haq bin Abdullah se riwayat kartey huey yun kaha : Abu-Umaiya jo ke Ansari aadmi they wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain."
4381,Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kehney laga : aey Allah ke Rasool ! maine had ka jurm kiya hai. (jurm qabile-had hai) mujh par had qayam farmaeyn . aapney farmaya : ''kya bhala to ne aatey waqt wuzu kiya tha?'' usney kaha : ji haan ! aapney farmaya : ''kya to ne hamarey sath mil kar Namaz padhi hai? '' usney kaha : ji haan ! aapney farmaya : '' jao Allah ne tujhey maaf kar diya hai.''
4382,"Azhar bin Abdullah Harazi se riwayat hai ke qabeela klaa' ke logon ka kuchh maal chori ho gaya. unhoney kuchh julaahon par uska ilzam lagaya. un logon ko Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) sahibe Rasool ke paas laya gaya to unhoney unko kaee din qaid mein rakha phir chhod diya. maal waley Hazrat Noman (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaye aur kaha : aapney un logon ko maarey peetey aur tehqiq aur chhaanbeen ke baghair hi chhod diya hai. to Hazrat Noman (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : tum kya chahtey ho? agar chaho to main unhen maarta hun, agar tumhara maal mil gaya to behtar , warna uska badla tumhari peethon se lunga. jis qadr unko maara hoga tumhen bhi maarunga. unhoney kaha : kya ye aap ka faisla hai? unhoney farmaya : ye Allah ka faisla hai aur Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka faisla hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Hazrat Noman (Raziallahu anhu) ne kulaaee logon ko apni is baat se daraya tha. aur maqsad ye wazeh karna tha ke mulzim ko aetiraaf ke baad hi maarna durust hai."
4383,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) chothai Dinar ya us se ziyada ki chori mein chor ka haath kaataa kartey they.
4384,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''chor ka haath chauthai Dinar ya us se ziyada mein kaataa jaey. Ahmed bin Saleh ke alfaz mein hai : ''haath ka kaatna chauthai Dinar aur us se ziyada mein hai.''
4385,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik dhaal ki chori mein haath kaataa tha jiski qeemat teen dirham thi.
4386,"Saiyedna Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik dhaal ki chori main eik aadmi ka haath kaataa , jo usney aurton waley suffa (aurton ke liye makhsus saya-daar maqam jahan wo Namaz waghaira padha karti thin) se churai thi. us dhaal ki qeemat teen dirham thi."
4387,Saiyedna ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik dhaal ke badley eik aadmi ka haath kaataa jiski qeemat eik Dinar ya das dirham thi. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is riwayat ko Muhammad bin Salma aur Sa'daan bin Yahya ne ibn Is'haq se iski sanad se riwayat kiya hai.
4388,"Muhammad bin Yahya bin Hibbaan ne bayan kiya ke eik ghulam ne kisi ke baagh se khajoor ka eik paudhaa chori karkey apney Malik ke baagh mein laga diya. paudhey wala apna paudhaa dhoondney nikla aur usey pa liya. phir us ghulam ka muqadma Marwan bin Hakam ke yahan pesh kar diya jo un dino Madiney ke ameer they. Marwan ne ghulam ko qaid kar liya aur chaha ke uska haath kaat dey. tab ghulam ka Malik Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan gaya aur un se ye masla puchha to unhoney bataya ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna tha, wo farmatey they : ''(darakhton par lagey) phal mein aur khajoor ki giri mein haath nahin kat'taa. ''to us aadmi ne kaha : tehqiq Marwan ne merey ghulam ko pakda hua hai aur wo uska haath kaatna chahta hai. aur main chahta hun ke aap merey sath uskey paas chalen aur jo hadees aapney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suni hai usey bhi bataeyn. chunanche Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) uskey sath gaey aur Marwan ke paas pahunchey aur uskey samney bayan kiya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : ''phal mein aur khajoor ki giri mein haath nahin kat'taa.'' chunanche Marwan ne hukm diya aur ghulam ko chhod diya gaya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke (الكثر) se murad khajoor ki wo naram giri hai jo uskey taney ke ooper kinarey mein hoti hai."
4389,Muhammad bin Yahya bin Hibbaan ne mazkura baala hadees bayan ki aur kaha : Marwan ne us ghulam ko chand kodey maarey aur chhod diya.
4390,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu Anhuma) riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha gaya ke darakhton par lagi khajuron ka kya hukm hai? to aapney farmaya : ''jo zarurat mand apney munh se kha ley , lekin pallu mein na baandhey to us par kuchh nahin, aur agar koi kuchh lekar nikley to us par uska do gunaa jurmaana aur saza hai, aur agar koi khaliyiaan mein mehfooz kar deney ke baad churaaey aur uski qeemat eik dhaal ko pahunchey to us mein haath ka kaatna hai. aur jo koi us se kam mein churaaey to us par chori shuda ka do gunaa jurmaana aur saza hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke (الجرين) se murad (jo khaan) hai, yani jahan khajoor waghaira khushk aur zakhira ki jati hai."
4391,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''luterey ka haath nahin kat'taa aur jo elaniya maal lutey wo ham mein se nahin.''"
4392,usi mazkura sanad se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''khayanat kerney waley ka haath nahin kat'taa.''
4393,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se usi hadees ke misl (jaisi) riwayat kya aur mazeed kaha : ''uchkkey ka haath nahin kat'taa. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke ye dono hadisein ibne-Juraij ne Abu-Zubair se nahin sunin hain. aur mujhey Imam Ahmed bin Hanbal (Rahimahullah) se ye baat pahunchi hai, unhoney kaha ke ye hadisen ibne-Juraij ne Yaseen Zayyat se suni hain. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : ye hadisen Mughira bin Muslim ne bhi ba-waaste Abu-Zubair, Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat ki hain."
4394,"Hazrat Safwan bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main masjid mein soyaa hua tha, mujh par eik munaqqash ooni chadar thi. jiski qeemat tees dirham thi. eik aadmi aaya aur usney ye chupkey se mujh se badi jaldi se nikal li. phir us aadmi ko pakad liya gaya aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas laya gaya. to aapney hukm diya ke uska haath kaat diya jaey. Hazrat Safwan (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kiya ke kya bhala sirf tees dirham ke badley mein aap uska haath kaatein gey? main usey isko farokht karta hun aur qeemat ki adaegi udhaar kar leta hun. aapney farmaya : ''tum ne ye isko merey paas laney se pehley kyon na kiya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ye riwayat ba-sand  (Zaayda an (an) Siamaak an (an) Juaid bin Hujair) yun hai : Hazrat Safwan so gaey. Taaus aur Mujahid ke alfaz mein yun hai ke wo soey huey they to eik chor aaya aur usney unki chadar unke sar ke nichey se churaa li aur Abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman ki riwayat mein hai ke usney ye chadar sar ke nichey se sar kaa li to wo jaag gaey aur shor machaya to usey pakad liya gaya. Zohri ne Safwan bin Abdullah se riwayat kartey huey kaha : Hazrat Safwan bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) masjid mein so gaey aur apni chadar ko apney sar ke nichey bator takiya rakh liya . eik chor aaya aur usney ye chadar uda li to unhoney usey pakad liya aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley aaey."
4395,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke bano makhzoom ki eik aurat chizen mang kar ley jati aur phir mukar jaya karti thi. chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hukm diya aur uska haath kaat diya gaya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is riwayat ko Juweriya ne ba-waaste Naafe , ibne-Umar se ya Safiya binte-Abi Ubaid se riwayat kya to is mein mazeed yun kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khutba deney ke liye khadey huey aur farmaya : ''kya koi aurat hai jo Allah aur uskey Rasool ki taraf tauba kar ley.'' aapney ye baat teen baar dohraee. jabkey wo aurat samney mojud dekh rahi thi , magar na wo uthi aur na boli . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke is riwayat ko ibne Ghanaj ne ba-waaste Naafe , Safiya binte Abu-Ubaid se bayan kiya is mein hai ke phir us par shahadat di gaee."
4396,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke eik aurat ne kaee maroof logon ke naam se kuch zewrat aariyatan liye jabke wo khud koi maroof na thi. phir wo zewrat usney bech daley , to pakad li gaee aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein laee gaee to aapney uska haath kaat deney ka hukm diya. aur ye wohi aurat hai jiskey baarey mein Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne sifarish ki thi aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is silsiley mein jo kuchh kehna tha kaha."
4397,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke bano makhzoom ki eik aurat maal mang kar ley jati aur phir myukar jati thi to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hukm diya ke uska haath kaat diya jaey aur wo qissa bayan kya jo (Qutaiba an (an) Lais (an) ibne Sihab) ki (guzishta) riwayat (4373) mein aaya hai. mazeed kaha ke phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uska haath kaat dala.
4398,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teen aadmiyon se qalam utha liya gaya hai : soyaa hua yahan tak ke jaag jaey, deewana yahan tak ke aql mand ho jaey aur bachchey se yahan tak ke bada (baligh) ho jaey.''"
4399,"Saiyedna ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas eik pagal aurat laee gaee jisney zina kiya tha. to unhoney uskey baarey mein Sahaba se mashwara kiya. aur phir hukm diya ke isey sangsaar kar diya jaey. Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) us aurat ke paas se guzrey , unhoney puchha ke iska kya maamla hai? logon ne kaha ke ye bano falan ki pagal aurat hai aur isney zina kiya hai aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne hukm diya hai ke isey sangsaar kar diya jaey. to unhon (Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu)) ne farmaya ke isey wapis ley jao aur khud Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan chaley aaye aur kaha : ameerul-momeneen ! kya aap nahin jantey ke teen tarah ke aadmiyon se qalam utha liya gaya hai : pagal, majnun se yahan tak ke sehat mand ho jaey, soey huey se yahan tak ke jaag jaey aur bachchey se yahan tak ke aql mand (baligh) ho jaey. unhoney kaha : kyon nahin. kaha : to phir kya wajeh hai ke is majnun aurat ko rajm kiya janey laga hai? Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : (ab to) is par kuchh nahin hoga. kaha ke phir isey chhod den. chunanche unhoney is aurat ko chhod diya. aur raawi ne kaha ke phir wo (Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu)) Allahu-Akbar, Allahu-Akbar kehney lagey."
4400,Wakee ne Aamash se mazkura baalaa-hadees ki manind riwayat kiya aur kaha : (bachchey se qalam utha liya gaya hai) yahan tak ke aql mand ho jaey aur majnun se bhi yahan tak ke us se ifaaqa (fayda) pa jaey. bayan kiya ke phir Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) takbir kehney lagey.
4401,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke log us aurat ko lekar Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas se guzrey. aur Usman (bin Abi Sheba) ki riwayat (4399) ke ham-maani bayan kiya. unhoney kaha : kya aap ko yaad nahin ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''teen afrad se qalam utha liya gaya hai : majnun jiski aql maghloob ho yahan tak ke ifaaqa (fayda) pa jaey aur soyaa hua yahan tak ke jaag jaey aur bachcha yahan tak ke baligh ho jaey.'' Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aapney baja kaha aur is aurat ko chhod diya.
4402,"Abu-Zibyaan Janbi ka bayan hai ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas eik aurat laee gaee jisney bad-kari ka irtikab (jurm) kiya tha. isliye unhoney usko sangsaar kerney ka hukm diya, chunanche Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) guzrey to unhoney usey pakda aur chhod diya. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko uski khabar mili to unhoney kaha : Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko merey paas bulao . wo aaye aur kaha : aey ameerul-momeneen ! aap yaqinan jantey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : '' teen aadmiyon se qalam utha liya gaya hai, bachchey se yahan tak ke baligh ho jaey aur soey huey se yahan tak ke jaag jaey aur majnun pagal se yahan tak ke sehat mand ho jaey.'' aur ye aurat bano falan ki hai aur pagal hai. shayad ke jisney uskey sath ye ye kiya hai to ye apni isi kaifiyat mein thi. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main ye nahin janta (ke ye usi kaifiyat , yani pagal pan mein iski murtakib (mujrim) hui hai) Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : janta to main bhi nahin hun."
4403,"Saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teen tarah ke aadmiyon se qalam utha liya gaya hai, soey huey se yahan tak ke jaag jaey, bachchey se yahan tak ke baligh ho jaey aur majnun se yahan tak ke aqlmand ho jaey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : is riwayat ko ibne-Juraij ne ba-waasta Qasim bin Yazid , Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kiya hai aur is mein lafz (الخرف) ka izafa kiya. yani wo aadmi jo bahut ziyada umr ki wajeh se aql aur shaoor ki kaifiyat par qayam na rehta ho."
4404,"Hazrat Atiya Qurzi (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main banu Qureza ke qaidiyon mein se tha, chunanche musalmanon ne dekhna shuru kya, yani jis jiskey (zere-naaf ( baal ug aaye they usey qatl kar diya gaya aur jiskey nahin ugey they usey qatl na kiya gaya , chunanche main un mein se tha jinkey baal nahin ugey they."
4405,Abdul-Malik bin Umair ne ye riwayat bayan ki. (Atiya ne ( kaha : unhoney merey zere-naf se kapda hataayaa aur paya ke merey baal nahin ugey hain to mujhey qaidiyon mein shamil kar diya.
4406,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uhud waley din unka jayeza liya jabkey unki umr chaudah saal thi to aapney unko jang mein shareek honey ki ijazat nahin di thi. aur phir khandaq waley din unka jayeza liya aur wo pandarah saal ke they to aapney unko ijazat dey di.
4407,Naafe kehtey hain ke maine ye hadees Hazrat umr bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahimahullah) ko bayan ki to unhoney kaha : bila-shuba bachchey aur badey mein yehi umr had faasil hai.
4408,"Junaada bin Abu-Umaiya kehtey hain ke ham Hazrat Basar bin Irtaat (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath main eik samandari muhim mein ja rahey they ke eik chor ko laya gaya. uska naam Masdar tha (meem ki zer ke sath) usney eik bakhti oontni churaai thi, to unhoney kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai : '' safar mein haath na kaatey jaeyn .'' agar ye baat na hoti to main uska haath kaat daalta."
4409,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : ''aey Abu-Zar !'' maine arz kiya : main hazir hun aey Allah ke Rasool ! aur Mutee farma hun ! farmaya : '' tera kya haal hoga jab logon ko maut aaeygi aur un halaat mein ghar eik ghulam ke badley mein milega?'' aur aap ki murad thi ''qabr'' . maine arz kiya : Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain, ya kaha ke jo Allah aur uska Rasool merey liye pasand farma den. aapney farmaya : ''sabr karna. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Hammad bin Abu Sulaiman ne kaha : kafan chor ka haath kaataa jaey, kyonkey wo maiyat ke ghar mein dakhil hota hai."
4410,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas eik chor laya gaya. aapney farmaya : ''isey qatl kar do.'' Sahaba ne arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! isney to chori ki hai. aapney farmaya : ''iska (haath) kaat do, chunanche uska (haath) kaat diya gaya. phir usey dobara laya gaya to aapney farmaya : ''isey qatl kar do.'' Sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! usney chori ki hai, aapney farmaya : ''iska (baayan paon) kaat do.'' chunanche kaat diya gaya. phir usey teesri baar laya gaya to aapney farmaya : ''isey qatl kar do.'' Sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! usney chori ki hai. aapney farmaya : ''iska (baayan haath) kaat do.'' phir chauthi-baar laya gaya. aapney farmaya : ''isey qatl kar do.'' Sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! isney chori ki hai. aapney farmaya : ''iska (daayan paon) kaat do.'' phir usey paanchwin baar laya gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''isey qatl kar do.'' Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke phir ham usey ley gaey aur usey qatl kar dala . phir usey ghaseet kar eik kunwen mein dal diya aur ooper se patthar maarey."
4411,Abdur-Rehman bin Maheereez se riwayat hai ke ham ne Hazrat Fazaala bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke kya chor ka haath uski gardan mein latka dena sunnat hai? to unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas eik chor ko laya gaya to uska haath kaat diya gaya. phir aapney uskey haath ke mutalliq hukm diya to uski gardan mein latka diya gaya.
4412,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab mamlook ghulam chori karey to usey bech dalo , chahey aadhey auqiya (bees dirham) se becho.''"
4413,"Janab Ikrima se riwayat hai ke aayat kareema : ({ وَاللَّاتِي يَأْتِينَ الْفَاحِشَةَ مِنْ نِسَائِكُمْ . . . }) ''tumhari aurton mein se jo koi bad-kari ( zina (ka irtikab (jurm) keren to un par apney mein se chaar gawah lao , agar wo gawahi den to un aurton ko gharon mein qaid rakho yahan tak ke unhen maut aa jaey ya Allah unke liye koi raasta nikal dey.'' ke silsiley mein Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne farmaya ke aayat kareema mein mard ka bayan aurat ke baad hai. phir un dono (mard aur aurat) ko jama kartey huey farmaya : ({ وَاللَّذَانِ يَأْتِيَانِهَا مِنْكُمْ فَآذُوهُمَا . . . }) ''aur tum mein se jo ye kaam keren to unhen eza (takleef) do , phir agar wo tauba kar lein aur apni islah kar lein to un se darguzar karo.''phir ye hukm ( sura Noor ki) is aayat se mansookh kar diya gaya jis mein sau kodey maarney ka bayan hai ({ الزَّانِيَةُ وَالزَّانِي فَاجْلِدُوا . . ۔}) ''zaani mard aur aurat her eik ko sau-sau kodey maaro.''"
4414,Ibne-Abi Najeeh ne Janab Mujahid se riwayat kiya ke ''Ssabeel'' (raastey) se murad had ka nazil karna hai. Sufiyan ne kaha : ''un dono ko saza do'' se murad ghair shaadi shuda mard aur aurat hain. aur ''unko ghar mein rokey rakh '' se murad shaadi shuda aurten hain.
4415,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujh se ley lo , mujh se ley lo . tehqiq Allah taala ne un aurton ke liye raah nikal di hai. agar shaadi shuda , shaadi shuda ke sath (mulawwis ho aur bad-kari) karey to so kodey hain aur patthar maarna hain, aur kunwaaraa kunwari ke sath karey to so kodey hain aur eik saal ke liye shehar badri hai.''"
4416,Janab Hasan Basri ne ba-sand Yahya is riwayat ke ham-maani bayan kartey huey kaha : ''sau kodey hain (ghair shaadi shuda ko) aur rajm (sangsaar) karna hai (shaadi shuda ko).''
4417,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye hadees bayan ki . to logon ne Saad bin Ubada se kaha : aey Abu-Saabit ! hudood nazil hui hain, agar tum apni biwi ke sath kisi ko pao to kya karogey? unhoney kaha : main talwaar se un dono ka kaam tamam kar dunga yahan tak ke dono thandey ho jaeyn . kya bhala mein chaar gawah dhoondney jaunga? tab tak to wo apna kaam kar jaeyga (bad-kari karkey bhag jaeyga). chunanche wo chaley aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan ikhattey huey aur kehney lagey : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya aapney Abu-Saabit ko dekha ke aisey aisey kehta hai? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(aisey-moqe par) talwaar ki gawahi kafi hai.'' phir farmaya : ''nahin, nahin. mujhey andesha hai ke koi (waisay hi) bahaalat nasha ya be-wajah ghairat uskey dar pai na ho jaey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is hadees ka ibtidaai (shuruati) hissey Wakee ne Fazal-bin Dalham sey, unhoney Janab Hasan sey, unhoney Qabisa bin Hurais sey, unhoney Salma bin Mohbiq sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kiya hai. halanke ye sanad ibne Muhabbaq ki us riwayat ki hai jis mein hai ke eik aadmi apni biwi ki londi se zina kar baitha tha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Fazal-bin Dalham haafiz nahin hai. ye waasit mein qassaab tha."
4418,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne khutba diya aur kaha : tehqiq Allah taala ne Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko haq ke sath Nabi banakar bheja aur un par apni kitab nazil ki . is nazil karda ( kitab ( mein rajm ki aayat bhi thi. ham ne usey padha hai aur yaad kiya hai. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne rajm (sangsaar) kiya hai aur unke baad ham ne bhi rajm (sangsaar) kiya hai. mujhey andesha hai ke kahin waqt guzarney ke sath-sath koi ye na kehney lagey ke rajm (sangsaar) wali aayat ham kitabullah mein nahin paatey hain, is tarah wo Allah ke nazil karda fariza ko tarak karkey gumrah na ho jaeyn. isliye jis kisi mard ya aurat ne zina kiya ho aur wo shaadi shuda ho aur gawahi Sabit ho jaey ya hamal ho ya aetraaf ho, to us par rajm (sangsaar) haq hai. Allah ki qasam ! agar ye baat na hoti ke log kahengey ke umr ne Allah ki kitab mein izafa kar diya hai to main us aayat ko kitabullah mein darj kar deta."
4419,"Janab Yazid bin Nuaim bin Bazal apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Maaiz bin Malik yateem ladka tha aur merey walid ki sarparasti mein tha. phir wo qabiley ki eik ladki ke sath zina kar baitha . to merey walid ne us se kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas jao aur jo kuchh tum ne kiya hai uski unhen khabar do , shayad wo terey liye istighfar karen. aur us se unka maqsad sirf yehi umeed thi ke usey koi raah mil jaey. chunanche wo hazir hua aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! maine zina kiya hai, lihaza Allah ki kitab ka hukm mujh par nafiz (laagu) farma dijiye . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se rukh pher liya . usney phir kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! maine zina kiya hai mujh par Allah ki kitab ka hukm nafiz farma dijiye. aapney us se rukh pher liya. to usney (teesri baar) phir kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! maine zina kiya hai. mujh par Allah ki kitab ka hukm nafiz kar dijiye. yahan tak ke usney chaar baar is tarah kaha to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tu ne chaar baar ye baat kahi hai, to ne kis ke sath kiya hai?'' kaha : falan ladki ke sath . aapney puchha : ''tu uskey sath ikhattey letaa hai?'' kaha : haan . aapney puchha : ''tu uskey sath chimta hai?'' kaha : haan . aapney puchha : ''tu ne uskey sath jima (sambhog) kiya hai?'' kaha : haan . chunanche aapney usko sangsaar kerney ka hukm diya. chunanche usko Harra ki taraf ley jaya gaya. jab usey patthar maarey gaey aur usney pattharon ki chot mehsoos ki to bardasht na kar paya aur bhag khada hua. to Hazrat Abdullah bin Unais ne usko pa liya, jabkey deegar sathi thak gaey they. to Abdullah ne usko oont ka paya nikal maara aur usey qatl kar diya, phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aa kar ye sab bayan kiya to aapney farmaya : ''tum ne usko chhod kyon na diya, shayad wo tauba kar leta aur Allah uski tauba qubul farma leta.''"
4420,"Janab Hasan bin Muhammad bin Ali bin Abu Talib ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka farman : ''tum ne usko chhod kyon na diya'' mujh ko qabeela Aslam ke kaee logon ne bayan kiya jinhen mein jhoot se muttahim (jis par jhoot wagaira ka ilzam laga ho) nahin samajhta. kaha ke merey liye ye hadees wazeh na thi. chunanche main Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke paas hazir hua aur un se kaha ke qabeela Aslam ke log ye bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( Maaiz ko rajm (sangsaar) karney waley) logon se kaha, jab unhoney Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bataya ke Maaiz ko jab pathar lagey to wo unki chot bardasht na kar saka to aapney farmaya : ''tum ne usko chhod kyon na diya.'' mein ye hadees samajh nahin saka hun. to Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey bhatijey ! main is hadees ke mutalliq sab logon se badh kar janta hun. mein un logon mein shamil tha jinhon ne usko rajm (sangsaar) kiya tha. jab ham usko lekar nikley aur usey pathar maarey aur usey patharon ki chot padi to wo cheekh utha : aey qom ! mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas wapis ley chalo , meri qom ne mujhey marwaa dala hai, unhoney mujhey meri jaan ke mutalliq dhoka diya hai, unhoney mujh se kaha tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tujhey qatl nahin karengey. magar ham us se peechhey na hatey yahan tak ke usey maar dala. phir jab ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunchey aur aap ko uski khabar di to aapney farmaya : ''tum ne usey chhod kyon na diya aur usey merey paas kyon na ley aaye.'' (gharz ye thi ke) Allah ke Rasool usko Sabit qadam rehney ka kehtey. (yani duniya ka azab , aakhirat ke muqabley mein halka aur aasan hai). lekin ye mafhoom ho ke aapney had chhod deney ki gharz se ye kaha ho, aisey nahin hai, chunanche tab main (Hasan bin Muhammad) hadees ka matlab samajh saka."
4421,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Maaiz bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha : beshak maine zina kya hai. to aapney us se rukh pher liya . usney kaee baar aisey kaha aur aap us se apna munh phertey rahey . phir aapney uski qom se puchha : ''kya ye majnun aur pagal hai? '' unhoney kaha : nahin, is mein aisi koi baat nahin hai. aapney us se puchha : ''kya to ne haqiqat mein uskey sath kiya hai? '' usney kaha : haan . to aapney uskey mutalliq hukm diya ke isey rajm (sangsaar) kar diya jaey. chunanche usey ley jaya gaya aur sangsaar kar diya gaya aur us par Namaze janaza na padhi."
4422,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke jab Maaiz bin Malik ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein laya gaya to maine usey dekha ke wo chhotey qad ka mota aadmi tha, us par chadar nahin thi. usney apney ooper chaar gawahiyan deen ke usney zina kiya hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se farmaya : ''shayad to ne uska bosa liya hoga?'' usney kaha : nahin Allah ki qasam ! is naalauaq ne zina kiya hai. chunanche aapney usey rajm (sangsaar) kiya (yani hukm diya ( phir aapney khutba diya aur farmaya : ''khabrdar ! ham jab Shan wale Allah ki raah (jihad) mein nikaltey hain to koi un mein peechhey reh jata hai, aisey aawaz nikalta hai jaisey ke bakra nikalta hai, phir kisi aurat ko thodi si koi chiz dey deta hai, khabrdar ! agar Allah ne mujh ko un mein se kisi par qudrat di to main usey nishane ibrat bana dunga.''"
4423,"Shoba ne Simaak se riwayat kiya, kaha ke maine Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) se ye hadees suni , jabkey pehley wali hadees ziyada kamil hai. kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko dobara wapis kiya. Simaak kehtey hain ke maine Saeed bin Jubair ko ye riwayat bayan ki to unhoney kaha ke aapney usko chaar baar lautaya tha."
4424,Shoba kehtey hain ke maine Janab Simaak se puchha ke (كثبة (ka kya mafhoom hai? unhoney kaha ke ''thoda sa doodh.''
4425,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Maaiz bin Malik se kaha : ''kya jo baat mujhey terey mutalliq pahunchi hai wo haq hai?'' bola ke aap ko merey mutalliq kya khabar pahunchi hai? aapney farmaya : ''mujhey maloom hua hai ke tum bano falan ki ladki ke sath zina kar baithey ho?'' kaha ke haan , chunanche usney chaar gawahiyan den. phir aapney uskey mutalliq hukm diya to usey rajm (sangsaar) kar diya gaya."
4426,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, unhoney kaha ke Hazrat Maaiz bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur usney zina ka aetraaf kiya, do baar , to aapney usko wapis bhagaa diya. wo phir aaya aur zina kerney ka do baar aetraaf kiya, tab aapney farmaya : ''tu ne apney ooper chaar baar shahadat di hai. isey ley jao aur rajm (sangsaar) kar do.''"
4427,"Saiyedna ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Maaiz bin Malik se kaha : ''shayad to ne bosa liya hoga, ya chutki bhari hogi ya (waisay hi) dekha hoga.'' usney kaha : nahin. aapney farmaya : ''kya bhala to ne us se haqiqat mein sambhog kiya hai? ''usney kaha : haan . tab aapney usko rajm (sangsaar) karney ka hukm diya. Musa (bin-Ismail) ki riwayat mein ibne-Abbas ka wasta mazkur nahin. aur ye lafz Wahab ke hain."
4428,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke (Maaiz) Aslami , Allah ke Nabi ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur apney mutalliq gawahi di ke wo eik aurat ke sath zina kar baitha ye gawahi usney apney khilaf chaar martaba di. her baar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us se apna munh pher letey they. phir wo paanchwin baar samney hua to aapney us se puchha : ''kya to ne haqiqat mein uske sath sambhog kiya hai? '' usney kaha : haan . aapney kaha : ''yahan tak ke tera zikr (khas ang) uski farj (sharm-gaah) mein ghayeb ho gaya tha ?'' usney kaha : haan . aapney kaha : ''kya bhala jis tarah salaai surmey-daani mein ghayeb ho jati hai aur dol ki rassi kunwen mein chali jati hai.'' usney kaha : haan . aapney phir puchha : ''kya bhala jantey bhi ho ke zina kya hota hai? '' usney kaha : haan , main us se haram kaam kar baitha hun jaisey ke shohar apni biwi se halal karta hai. aapney farmaya : ''tu apni is baat se kya chahta hai? '' usney kaha : main chahta hun ke aap mujhey paak kar den. tab aapney hukm diya to isey rajm (sangsaar) kiya gaya. phir aapney apney Sahaba mein se do aadmiyon ko suna ke eik doosrey se keh rahe the : usko dekho ke Allah ne us par parda dala tha magar uskey nafs ne usko nahin chhoda yahan tak ke pattharon se maara gaya jaisey ke kuttey ko maara jata hai, to aap un se khamosh rahey . phir aap kuchh der chaltey rahey yahan tak ke eik murda gadhey ke paas se guzrey jiski taangein ooper ko uthi hui thi. aapney farmaya : ''falan aur falan kahan hain?'' unhoney kaha : ham ye rahey, aey Allah ke Rasool ! aapney farmaya : ''utro aur is murdar gadhey ka gosht khao.'' unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! bhala ye bhi koi khata hai? aapney farmaya : '' abhi jo tum ne apney bhai ki izzat paamaal ki hai, wo iskey khaney se badtar hai. qasam us zaat ki jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! bila-shuba wo ab jannat ki nehron mein dubkiyaan laga raha hai.''"
4429,"Abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ke chacha zaad se riwayat kiya, usney Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se mazkura baala hadees ki manind bayan kiya aur mazeed kaha ke raawiyon ne ikhtilaf kiya hai. baaz ne kaha ke usey darkht se baandha gaya aur baaz ne kaha ke usey khada kiya gaya."
4430,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke qabeela Aslam ka eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya. usney aa kar zina kerney ka aetraaf kiya, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se munh mod liya . usney phir aetraaf kiya, to aapney aeraz kar liya yahan tak ke usney apney ooper chaar gawahiyan den. tab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se kaha : ''kya to majnun hai? '' bola nahin. aapney puchha : ''kya to shaadi shuda hai? '' kehney laga : haan , tab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey mutalliq hukm diya to usko eid gaah mein rajm (sangsaar) kar diya gaya. phir jab usey zor zor se pathar padney lagey to wo daud bhaagaa, isliye usey ja liya gaya aur patthar maarey gaey yahan tak ke mar gaya. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey mutalliq achhi baat kahi magar uska janaza nahin padha."
4431,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha ke jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Maaiz bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ke rajm (sangsaar) karney ka hukm farmaya to ham usey Baqee ki taraf ley chaley , Allah ki qasam ! na ham ne usko baandha aur na uskey liye gadha khodaa. lekin wo hamarey samney khada ho gaya. Abu-Kaamil ne kaha ke ham ne usey haddiyan , dheley aur theekrey maarey to wo bhag khada hua aur ham bhi uskey peechhey bhag liye yahan tak ke wo Harra (pathreeli-zameen) ki janib mein aa gaya aur hamarey samney khada ho gaya to ham ne usey us jagah ke badey badey pathar maarey yahan tak ke wo thanda ho gaya. raawi ne kaha ke phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey liye na istighfar kiya aur na kisi tarah se bura bhala kaha."
4432,"Jareeri ne Abu-Nazara se riwayat kartey huey kaha ke eik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya . aur mazkura baala hadees ki manind riwayat kiya, lekin uski riwayat mukammal nahin hai. raawi ne kaha ke : log usey gaaliyaan deney lagey , to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko mana kiya. (phir) wo uskey liye istighfar karney lagey , to aapney unko mana kar diya aur kaha : ''ye aisa aadmi hai jisney gunah ka irtikab kiya hai aur Allah hi iska hisab leney wala hai.''"
4433,Janab Sulaiman bin Barida apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Maaiz bin Malik ka munh soonghaa tha (ke kahen sharab na pi rakhi ho).
4434,"Janab Abdullah bin Barida apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba kaha kartey they : kash ghaamidi aurat aur Maaiz bin Malik aetraaf ke baad hi ruju kar letey. . . . ya yun kaha agar wo dono aetraaf ke baad aap ki khidmat mein na aatey . . . . to aap unko talab na kartey , aapney unko chauthey aetraaf par rajm (sangsaar) kiya tha."
4435,"Hazrat Lajlaaj (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke wo baazar mein baithey kaam kar rahey they ke eik aurat bachchey ko uthaey guzri , to log josh mein uth khadey huey aur uthney walon mein main bhi utha aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahuncha . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us aurat se daryaft farma rahey they : ''ye jo (bachcha) terey sath hai iska baap kon hai? ''to wo khamosh rahi. eik jawan jo uskey sath tha bola : main iska baap hun, aey Allah ke Rasool ! aap us aurat ki taraf mutawajjeh huey aur puchha : ''ye jo (bachcha) terey sath hai iska baap kon hai? '' is jawan ne kaha : main iska baap hun, aey Allah ke Rasool ! to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey ird-gird khadey logon ki taraf dekha, aap un se is jawan ke mutalliq poochh rahey they, to unhoney kaha : ham iskey mutalliq achchha hi jantey hain. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se puchha : ''kya to shaadi shuda hai? '' usney kaha : haan , tab aapney uskey mutalliq hukm diya to usey rajm (sangsaar) kar diya gaya. raawi ne kaha : ham usey lekar nikley aur uskey liye gadha khodaa aur usko us mein gaad diya. phir patharon se maara yahan tak ke wo thanda ho gaya. phir eik aaya jo us sangsaar shuda ke mutalliq poochhney laga . ham usko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas ley gaey aur ham ne arz kiya ke ye aadmi aaya hai aur us khabees ke mutalliq poochhtey hai to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo to Shan Wale Allah kastoori ki khushbu se badh kar pakizah hai.'' tab maloom hua ke wo aadmi uska walid tha, to ham ne uski us sangsaar shuda ke ghusl aur kafan dafn mein madad ki . raawi ne kaha : mujhey yaad nahin ke Namaz ka bhi kaha ya nahin? aur ye riwayat Abda ki hai aur kamil hai."
4436,Khalid bin Lajlaaj ne apney walid se unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se is hadees ka kuchh hissey riwayat kiya.
4437,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur aap ke samney iqrar kiya ke usney eik aurat ke sath bad-kari ki hai, usney us aurat ka naam bhi liya , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us aurat ko bula bheja aur us-se is waqiye ke mutalliq puchha to usney bad-kari se inkar kiya. chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us aadmi ko had ke (sau) kodey lagaey aur us aurat ko chhod diya."
4438,"Saiyedna Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs ne eik aurat ke sath bad-kari ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey mutalliq hukm diya to usey had ke kodey maarey gaey . phir bataya gaya ke wo shaadi shuda hai to aapney hukm diya to usey sangsaar kiya gaya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is hadees ko Muhammad bin Bakr Barsaai ne ibne Juraih se Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) par moquf riwayat kiya hai. aur Abu-Aasim ne ibn Juraih sey, ibne-Wahab ki manind riwayat kiya aur usney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka zikr nahin kiya. kaha ke eik aadmi ne zina kiya to uskey shaadi shuda honey ka maloom na hua to usko kodey maarey gaey. phir maloom hua ke wo shaadi shuda hai to rajm (sangsaar) kiya gaya."
4439,Janab Abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya ke eik aadmi ne eik aurat se bad-kari ki aur maloom na hua ke wo shaadi shuda hai to usko kodey maarey gaey . phir maloom hua ke wo shaadi shuda hai to usko rajm (sangsaar) kiya gaya.
4440,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik aurat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aai . . . . Aban ki riwayat mein hai ke wo qabeela juhaina se thi. . . . usney kaha ke maine zina kiya hai aur hamal se hun. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey wali ko talab kiya aur us se farmaya : ''uskey sath achchha sulook karna aur jab bachchey ki wiladat ho jaey to is (aurat) ko ley aana.'' chunanche jab bachchey ki wiladat ho gaee to wo usey ley aaya . to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hukm diya aur us par uskey kapdey sakht karkey baandh diye gaey, phir aapney uskey mutalliq hukm diya aur usey rajm (sangsaar) kar diya gaya. phir aapney unhen hukm diya to unhoney us par Namaz (janaza) padhi. Aban sey, ''kapdey sakht karkey baandhney'' ki baat marwi (bayan) nahin hai."
4441,"Janab Auzaai se marwi (bayan) hai, unhoney kaha ke us par uskey kapdey sakht karkey baandhey gaey."
4442,"Janab Abdullah bin Barida apney walid Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke banu-Ghamid ki eik aurat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aai aur kehney lagi ke maine bad-kari ki hai. aapney farmaya : ''wapis chali ja.'' to wo laut gaee. phir jab aglaa din hua to wo aap ke paas aa gaee aur boli : shayad aap mujhey usi tarah lauta dena chahtey hain jis tarah aapney Maaiz bin Malik ko wapis kiya tha. Allah ki qasam ! main hamila hun (yani zina sey) aapney us se farmaya : ''ja wapis chali ja.'' to wo laut gaee . phir jab aglaa din hua to wo phir aap ki khidmat mein aa gaee to aapney us se farmaya : ''wapis chali ja yahan tak ke terey bachchey ki wiladat ho jaey.'' to wo wapis laut gaee. jab bachcha paida hua to wo bachchey ko lekar aa gaee aur kehney lagi : ye raha wo , isko maine janm diya hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se farmaya : '' wapis ja aur usko doodh pila yahan tak ke to iska doodh chhuda dey.'' wo phir usey lekar aai jabke usney iska doodh chhuda diya tha, bachchey ke haath mein koi chiz thi jisey wo kha raha tha. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bachchey ke mutalliq hukm diya jo musalmanon mein se eik aadmi ke hawaley kar diya gaya aur aapney us aurat ke mutalliq hukm diya to uskey liye gadha khodaa gaya aur hukm diya to usey rajm (sangsaar) kar diya gaya. aur Hazrat Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) un logon mein they jo usey pathar maar rahey they. unhoney usko eik pathar maara to us se khoon ka eik qatra unke rukhsaar par ja laga , iski wajeh se unhoney usko bura bhala kaha to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se farmaya : '' Khalid zara thehro (us ko bura bhala mat kaho) qasam us zaat ki jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! usney is qadr tauba ki hai ke agar koi zalim bhatta leney wala bhi is qadr tauba karta to bakhsh diya jata.'' aur aapney iskey mutalliq hukm diya, chunanche is par Namaz (janaza) padhi gaee aur phir usey dafn bhi kiya gaya."
4443,"Ibne-Abi bakra apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aurat ko rajm (sangsaar) kiya to uskey liye seeney tak gadha khodaa gaya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : mujhey ye hadees eik aadmi ne samjhai.  (wo Usman se jaisa ki haq tha nahin samajh sakey they.) Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne (mazeed) kaha ke , Ghassaani ne kaha ke juhaina , ghaamid aur baariq teeno eik hi qabiley (ke naam) hain."
4444,Zakariya bin Saleem ne apni sanad se mazkura baala hadees ki manind riwayat kiya aur mazeed kaha : phir (Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne) usey eik kankari maari jaisey ke chuna ho aur farmaya : ''maaro lekin chehra bachao.'' jab wo thandi ho gaee to usko gadhey se nikala aur us par Namaz (janaza) padhi aur uski tauba mein is tarah bayan kya jaisey ke Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees (4442) mein hai.
4445,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira aur Zaid bin Khalid Juhni (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke do aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein apna jhagda lekar aaye . eik ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham mein Allah ki kitab ke mutabiq faisla kar den. aur doosrey ne kaha . . . . aur wo us se badh kar samajhdaar tha. . . . haan aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham mein Allah ki kitab ke mutabiq faisla farma den aur mujhey ijazat den ke baat karun. aapney farmaya : ''kaho.'' usney kaha : mera beta is shakhs ke yahan naukar tha. . . . Aseef ke maani hain, naukar , mazdoor . . . . to usney iski biwi ke sath zina kiya. logon ne mujhey bataya ke merey bete par rajm (sangsaar) hai, maine uski taraf se sau bakriyan aur apni eik londi fidya di hai. phir maine ehle-ilm se maloom kiya to unhoney mujhey bataya ke merey bete par sau kodey aur eik saal ke liye shehar badri hai aur sangsaari iski biwi par hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qasam us zaat ki jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! main tum mein Allah taala ki kitab ke mutabiq faisla karunga. teri bakriyan aur teri londi tujhey wapis hongi.'' aur iskey ladkey ko sau kodey lagaey aur eik saal ke liye shehar Badr kar diya aur Unais Aslami ko farmaya ke doosrey ki biwi ke paas jaey, agar wo aetraaf kar ley to usko sangsaar kar dey, chunanche usney aetraaf kar liya to usney usko sangsaar kar diya."
4446,"Saiyedna ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke kuchh yahudi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye aur aap ko bataya ke hamarey eik mard aur aurat ne bad-kari ki hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se puchha : ''tum log zina ke silsiley mein Taurat mein kya paatey ho?'' unhoney kaha : ham unhen be-izzat kartey hain aur unhen kodey maarey jatey hain. to Hazrat Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke tum jhoot kehtey ho. bila-shuba us mein rajm (sangsaar) ka hukm hai. chunanche wo Taurat ley aaye aur usey khola to un mein se eik ne apna haath rajm (sangsaar) wali aayat par rakh liya , phir uskey aagey peechhey se padhney laga. to Hazrat Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se kaha : apna haath utha. usney haath uthaya to us mein rajm (sangsaar) wali aayat mojud thi. to wo boley : sach hai aey Muhammad ! (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) is mein rajm (sangsaar) ki aayat mojud hai. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unke mutalliq hukm diya aur unhen sangsaar kar diya gaya. Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke maine us mard ko dekha ke wo us aurat ko patharon se bachaney ke liye us par jhuktaa tha."
4447,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas se eik yahudi ko lekar guzrey , uska chehra kaalaa kiya hua tha aur wo usey ghumaa phira rahey they. to aapney unhen qasmen de-kar un se puchha : '' tumhari kitab mein zaani ki had kya hai? '' unhoney ye baat apney eik aadmi ki taraf tahweel kar di. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko qasam de-kar puchha : '' tumhari kitab mein zaani ki had kya hai? '' usney kaha : sangsaar karna , lekin jab hamarey shareefon mein zina kaarii aam ho gaee , to ham ne namunasib jana ke shareef (sahibe-haisiyat) ko chhod diya jaey aur ghatiya (ghareeb) par had qaaim ki jaey, so ham ne isko tarak kar diya. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey mutalliq hukm diya aur usey rajm (sangsaar) kar diya gaya. phir farmaya : ''aey Allah ! main wo pehla shakhs hun jo teri kitab ke is hukm ko zinda kar raha hun jisey unhoney murda kar chhoda tha.''"
4448,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas se eik aisey yahudi ka guzar hua jis ka munh kaalaa kiya hua tha aur usko maara bhi ja raha tha, aapney un logon ko bulaya aur puchha : ''kya tum zaani ki had aisey hi paatey ho?'' unhoney kaha : haan . to aapney unke eik aalim ko bulaya aur us se farmaya : ''main tujhey us Allah ki qasam de-kar poochhta hun jisney Hazrat Musa Alehissalam par Taurat nazil ki ! kya tum apni kitab mein zaani ki had aisey hi paatey ho?'' usney kaha : ya Allah ! nahin. agar aapney mujhey ye qasam na di hoti to main aap ko na batata. ham apni kitab mein zaani ki had rajm (sangsaar) hi paatey hain, lekin hamarey shareefon mein ye zina bahut badh gaya to ham jab kisi shareef (baa-asar shakhs) ko pakadtey to chhod detey they aur agar kamzor ko pakadtey to us par had qaaim kar detey they. phir ham ne kaha : aao kisi aisi baat par muttafiq ho jaeyn jo ham shareef aur kamzor sab par nafiz (laagu) kar saken. chunanche ham munh kaalaa karney aur dhool-dhappe par muttafiq ho gaey aur rajm (sangsaar) karna chhod diya, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! main wo pehla aadmi hun jo terey hukm ko zinda kar raha hun jabkey inhoney isko murda kar chhoda tha.'' phir aapney is zaani ke mutalliq hukm diya to usey rajm (sangsaar) kar diya gaya. isliye Allah taala ne (Sura Maayda ki) aayaat (41 taa 47 ( nazil farmaee.  (tarjama) ''aey Rasool ! jo log kufr mein jaldi kartey hain aap unke baarey mein gham na karen. . . taa . . . wo kehtey hain ke agar tum ko ye hukm miley (kodey maarney ka ( to qubul kar lena. agar ye na miley to us se door rehna . . . taa . . . aur jo Allah ke nazil karda ke mutabiq faisla na keren to wo kafir hain. . . . ye yahudiyon ke baarey mein hai. . taa . . . aur jo Allah ke nazil karda ke mutabiq faisla na keren to wo zalim hain. ye yahudiyon ke baarey mein hai. . taa . . . aur jo Allah ke nazil karda ke mutabiq faisla na keren to wo fasiq hain. . .''  ye sab aayaat kuffar ke mutalliq hain."
4449,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke yahudiyon ki eik jamaat aai aur wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko wadi quf mein bula ley gaey . to aap unke paas eik ghar mein gaey jo unka madrasa tha. unhoney kaha : aey Abul-Qaasim ! ham mein se eik aadmi ne eik aurat se zina kiya hai, so aap un mein faisla kar den. unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye eik takiya rakh diya, aap us par tashrif farma huey . phir farmaya : '' Taurat ley aao.'' to usey ley aaya gaya. aapney takiya apney nichey se nikala aur Taurat ko is par rakha . phir farmaya : ''main tujh par emaan laya hun aur us zaat par bhi jisney tujhey utaara hai.'' phir farmaya : ''apna bada aalim ley aao.'' to eik nojawan ko ley aaya gaya. phir rajm (sangsaar) ka qissa bayan kiya jaisey ke Malik an (an) Naafe ki hadees (4446) mein bayan hua hai."
4450,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai aur ye Maamer ki riwayat hai aur ziyada kamil hai, unhoney kaha ke yahudiyon main eik mard aur aurat ne zina kiya to un mein se baaz ne baaz se kaha : chalo us Nabi ke paas chaltey hain, beshak ye Nabi hai jo narmi aur kami ke sath mab'oos (bheja) hua hai. agar usney rajm (sangsaar) ke alawa koi aur fatwa diya to ham usey qubul kar lengey aur usko Allah ke yahan daleel bana lengey. ham kahengey ke ye terey eik Nabi ka fatwa tha. chunanche wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye jabkey aap masjid mein apney Sahaba ke sath tashrif farma they. kehney lagey : aey Abul-Qaasim ! aap ki aisey mard aur aurat ke baarey mein kya raey hai jinhon ne zina kiya ho? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se koi baat na ki yahan tak ke aap unke us ghar mein aaye jis mein unka madrasa tha. aap darwazey par khadey huey aur farmaya : ''main tumhen us Allah ki qasam deta hun jisney Hazrat Musa Alehissalam par Taurat nazil ki hai, tum log shaadi shuda zaani ke mutalliq Taurat mein kya paatey ho?'' unhoney kaha ke munh kaalaa kiya jaey, gadhey par ulta karkey bithaya jaey aur maara peetaa jaey. . . .) التجبية (ke maani ye hain ke dono zina-kaaron ko gadhey par yun bithaya jaey ke unki pusht eik doosrey ki taraf ho aur unhen phiraayaa jaey. . . . aur eik nau-jawan un mein khamosh raha. jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko khamosh dekha to aapney usko badi sakht qasam di. to usney kaha : aey Allah . . . . ! jab aapney hamein qasam de-di hai to (haqeeqat ye hai ke) ham Taurat mein rajm (sangsaar) hi paatey hain. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''is baat ki ibtida (shuruat) kaisey hui ke tum logon ne Allah ke hukm mein rukhsat (choot) apna li?'' usney kaha ke hamarey eik badshah ke qaribi ne zina kiya to usney rajm (sangsaar) ko us se taal diya. phir eik doosrey qabiley mein kisi ne zina kiya to usney usko rajm (sangsaar) karna chaha. to uski qom uskey aadey aa gaee aur kehney lagi ke jab tak tum apna aadmi na lao aur usey rajm (sangsaar) na kar do hamarey aadmi ko rajm (sangsaar) nahin kiya jaeyga. chunanche unhoney aapas mein is saza par ittifaq kar liya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main Taurat ke mutabiq faisla karta hun, chunanche aapney un dono ke mutalliq hukm diya to unhen rajm (sangsaar) kar diya gaya. Zohri (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : hamein ye baat pahunchi hai ke Sura Maayda ki aayat : 44 ({ إِنَّا أَنْزَلْنَا التَّوْرَاةَ فِيهَا هُدًى وَنُورٌ يَحْكُمُ بِهَا النَّبِيُّونَ الَّذِينَ أَسْلَمُوا }) unhin ke silsiley mein utri thi. aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) inhi mein se they. (jo Allah ke hukm bardar aur hidayat aur Noor ke mutabiq faisla karney waley they.)"
4451,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke yahudiyon ke eik mard aur aurat ne zina kiya jo shaadi shuda they. . . . aur ye un dino ki baat hai jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina tashrif ley aaye they. . . . aur un yahudiyon mein Taurat ke mutabiq (zaaniyon par) rajm (sangsaar) farz tha, magar unhoney usey chhod kar unhen zaleel aur ruswa karna ikhtiyar kar liya tha ke usey tarkol lagi rassi se sau baar maara jaey aur gadhey par pichli janib munh karkey bithaya jaey. to unke kaee ulama ikhattey huey aur unhoney doosrey kuchh logon ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas bheja ke aap se zaani ki had ke mutalliq poochhen aur hadees bayan ki. is mein kaha ke . . . chunkey wo ehale yahood aap ke deen par na they ke aap unka faisla kartey, isliye aap ko is mein ikhtiyar diya gaya , farmaya : ({ فَإِنْ جَاءُوكَ فَاحْكُمْ بَيْنَهُمْ أَوْ أَعْرِضْ عَنْهُمْ }) ''agar wo aap ke paas aa-jaeyn to un mein faisla keren ya aeraz kar (bach) jaeyn .''"
4452,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke yahudi apney eik mard aur aurat ko lekar aaye jinhon ne zina kiya tha. to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney do badey aalimon ko ley aao.'' isliye wo Sooriyaa ke do beton ko ley aaye , aapney unhen qasam de-kar puchha ke tum unke baarey mein Taurat mein kya paatey ho? to unhoney kaha : Taurat mein ham ye paatey hain ke jab chaar aadmi gawahi dey den ke unhoney mard ke zakar (khas ang) ko aurat ki farj (sharmgaah) mein aisey dekha hai jaisey surmey daani mein silaai hoti hai to unhen rajm (sangsaar) kar diya jaey. aapney farmaya : ''to tumhen inko rajm (sangsaar) karney mein kya maane (rukawat) hai?'' unhoney kaha : hamari apni hukoomat to nahin hai isliye qatl karna hamen bura lagta hai. tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne gawah talab kiye to wo chaar gawah lekar aaye. unhoney gawahi di ke unhoney mard ke zakar (khas ang) ko aurat ki farj mein aisey dekha hai jaisey surmey daani mein silaai ho, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko rajm (sangsaar) karney ka hukm diya."
4453,Ibrahim aur Shobi ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se iski manind riwayat kiya. magar is mein gawahon ko talab karney aur unke gawahi deney ka bayan nahin hai.
4454,Ibne Shabarma ne Shobi se iski manind riwayat kiya.
4455,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne yahudiyon ke eik mard aur aurat ko , jinhon ne zina kiya tha, rajm (sangsaar) karwaya tha."
4456,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik dafa main apney gumshuda oont dhoond raha tha ke oont sawaron ya ghud sawaron ka eik qafila aaya, unke sath jhandaa tha. chunkey mujhey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan eik maqam hasil tha is wajeh se Erab (dehaati) log merey ird-gird phirney lagey . phir wo eik qubba par aaye , wahan se unhoney eik mard ko nikala aur uski gardan uda di. maine uskey mutalliq puchha to unhoney bataya ke usney apney baap ki biwi ke sath nikah kiya hai."
4457,"Janab Yazid bin Bara apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : main apney chacha se mila jabke unke paas jhandaa tha. maine un se puchha : kahan ka irada hai? unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey eik aadmi ki taraf bheja hai jisney apney baap ki biwi ke sath nikah kiya hai, aapney mujhey hukm diya hai ke main uski gardan maar dun aur uska maal ley-lun."
4458,"Habib bin Salim se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs jis ka naam Abdur-Rehman bin Hunain tha apni biwi ki londi ke sath mulawwis ho gaya. uska muqadma Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) ke samney pesh kiya gaya jabkey wo koofa ke ameer they. to unhoney kaha : main terey baarey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wala faisla karunga . agar us (aurat) ne us londi ko terey liye halal kar diya to main tujhey sau kodey maarunga , agar wo halal na karey to patharon se sangsaar karunga. chunanche us aurat ne usey iskey liye halal kar diya. to Hazrat Noman (Raziallahu anhu) ne isko sau kodey maarey. Janab Qatada ne kaha : maine Habib bin Salim ko likha to unhoney mujhey ye riwayat likh bheji."
4459,Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kiya ke : ''jo shakhs apni biwi ki londi ki sath mulawwis ho jaey to agar biwi ne usey uskey liye halal kar diya ho to us ( shohar ( ko so kodey maarey jaeyn aur agar halal na karey to main usey rajm (sangsaar) karunga.''
4460,"Hazrat Salma bin Mohbiq (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jo shakhs apni biwi ki londi se mulawwis ho gaya ho, is silsiley mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne faisla farmaya tha ke agar us shohar ne londi ko majboor kiya ho to wo londi azad hogi , aur us (shohar) par lazim hoga ke uski maalika ko usi jaisi londi mohaiyya karey. aur agar londi khud se razi thi to ye usi (shohar) ki hui aur shohar par lazim hoga ke uski maalika ko usi jaisi londi la kar dey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Yunus bin Ubaid , Amr bin Dinar , Mansoor bin Azan aur Salam ne Hasan Basri se ye hadees mazkura baala riwayat ke ham-maani bayan ki hai. Yunus aur Mansoor ne apni sanad mein Qabisa (bin Hurais) ka zikr nahin kiya."
4461,Hazrat Salma bin Mohbiq (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura baala hadees ki manind riwayat kiya. magar yun kaha ke agar londi razi thi to ye us shohar ki hui aur uski qeemat ke barabar maal uski maalika ko dena hoga.
4462,"Saiyedna ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisey tum pao ke wo qaume-Loot ka sa amal kartey hain to faail (karta) aur mafool (karm) (dono) ko qatl kar do. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Sulaiman bin Bilal ne ba-waaste Amr bin Abu-Amr isi ki manind riwayat kiya. aur Ibad bin Mansoor ne ba-waaste Ikrima , Hazrat ibne-Abbas se marfooan riwayat kiya. isi ke sath ibne-Juraij ne ba-sand Ibrahim, Dawud bin Husain, ibne-Abbas se marfooan riwayat kiya."
4463,"Janab Saeed bin Jubair aur Mujahid, Saiyedna ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat kartey hain ke kunwaaraa agar qome-Loot ka sa kaam karta paya jaey, to usey sangsaar kiya jaey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Aasim (Aasim bin Abi Najood) ki hadees (jo aagey aa rahi hai. 4465 ( Amr bin Abi Amr ki hadees (4464) ko zaeef karti hai."
4464,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo koi kisi chaupaey se bura kaam karey us shakhs ko qatl kar do aur uskey sath us chaupaey ko bhi maar dalo.'' (Ikrima kehtey hain) maine un (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma)) se kaha ke chaupaey ke qatl ki wajeh kiya hai? kaha ke mera khayal hai ke aapney makruh jana ke uska gosht khaya jaey jabkey uskey sath aisa kaam kiya gaya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ye riwayat qawi nahin hai."
4465,"Abu-Rizeen , Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat kartey hain ke jo shakhs chaupaey se bura kaam karey us par had nahin hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Ata ne bhi aisey hi kaha hai. Hakam kehtey hain ke usko kodey lagaey jaeyn magar is tadaad mein ke had ko na pahunchein. Hasan Basri (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke aisa aadmi zaani ki manind hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Aasim ki hadees Amr bin Abu-Amr ki riwayat (4464) ko zaeef karti hai."
4466,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, eik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya. usney eik aurat ke sath zina karney ka iqrar kiya. usney aap ke samney us aurat ka naam bhi liya, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us aurat ko bulwaya aur us se uskey baarey mein puchha to aurat ne zina se inkar kiya. to aapney us shakhs ko had ke kodey lagaey aur aurat ko chhod diya."
4467,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke qabeela Bakr bin Leis ka eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya aur iqrar kiya ke usney eik aurat ke sath zina kiya hai. usney chaar baar ye iqrar kiya. to aapney usko sau kodey lagaey. isliye ke wo ghair shaadi shuda tha. phir us se aurat par gawahi li, to aurat ne kaha : Allah ki qasam ! aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye jhoot boltaa hai. phir aapney usko tohmat ki had assi kodey lagai."
4468,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, eik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kehney laga : beshak Madiney se bahir maine eik aurat se boss aur kinaar kiya hai, magar mujaamiat (sambhog) nahin ki hai aur ab mein aap ke samney hazir hun to jo chahey mujhey saza den. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ne teri parda poshi ki thi , agar to bhi apney aap par parda daley rakhta (to behtar tha). to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko koi jawab na diya. to wo aadmi chala gaya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey peechey aadmi bheja aur usey talab kiya, phir us par ye aayat tilawat farmaai :({ وَأَقِمِ الصَّلَاةَ طَرَفَيِ النَّهَارِ وَزُلَفًا مِنَ اللَّيْلِ . . . }) ''din ke dono atraaf (siron) mein Namaz qaaim karo aur raat ke oqaat mein bhi. bila-shuba nekiyan, buraiyon ko khatam kar deti hain, ye nasihat hai nasihat hasil kerney walon ke liye.'' qom mein se eik aadmi bola : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya ye usi ke liye khas hai ya sab logon ke liye hai? aapney farmaya : ''sabhi logon ke liye hai.''"
4469,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira aur Zaid bin Khalid Juhni (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha gaya ke ghair shaadi shuda londi agar zina karey to (us ka kiya hukm hai)? aapney farmaya : ''agar zina karey to usey kodey lagao. agar phir zina karey to usey kodey lagao. agar phir zina karey to kodey lagao. agar phir zina karey to usey bech dalo , chahey (chahe) eik rassi hi ke badley ho. ibne-Shahab ne kaha : mujhey nahin maloom ke teesri baar mein kaha ya chauthi baar ye kaha (ke usey bech dalo). aur (الضفير) ke maani hain,rassi.''"
4470,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ki londi zina karey to chahiye ke usey had lagaey aur aar (sharm) na dilaaey aur teen baar tak aisa karey, agar chauthi baar bhi karey to usey had lagaey aur eik rassi ke badley bech daley.'' ya farmaya : ''baalon ki rassi ke iwaz bech dey.''"
4471,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye hadees riwayat ki. is par har baar yun kaha : ''usey maarey. (had lagaey) ye Allah ki kitab ka hukm hai aur aar (sharm) mat dilaaey (yani sharm dilaney par kifaayat na karey).'' aur chauthi baar farmaya : ''agar phir bhi aisa karey to usey maarey, ye kitabullah ka hukm hai, phir usey farokht kar daley chahey (chahe) baalon ki rassi ke badley hi ho.''"
4472,"Janab Abu-Umama bin Sehal bin Hanif kehtey hain ke un se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baaz Ansari sahaabiyon ne bayan kiya ke unka eik aadmi bimar ho gaya aur is qadr kamzor ho gaya ke bas haddiyon par chamdaa reh gaya. uskey paas kisi ki londi aai , usey dekh kar usey josh aa gaya aur phir us se jima (sambhog) kar baitha. jab uski qom ke log uski iyaadat ke liye gaey to usney unhen apni ye baat batai aur kaha ke merey mutalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se daryaft karo, beshak merey paas eik londi aai thi aur main us se jimaa (sambhog) kar baitha hun. chunanche unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uska zikr kiya aur bataya ke ham ne us jaisa bimar koi nahin dekha, agar ham usey aap ke paas utha kar bhi laeyn to uski haddiyan juda ho jaeyngi , wo to bas haddiyon par chamdaa hai, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''uskey liye khajoor ki eik aisi dali hasil karo jis mein bareek sau shaakhen hon, wo usey eik hi maar do.''"
4473,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke aale Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki eik londi ne bad-kari ki . aapney farmaya : ''aey Ali ! jao aur usko had lagao.'' kehtey hain ke main chala to maloom hua ke us se khoon beh raha hai jo rukta hi nahin hai. main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aa gaya. aapney puchha : ''aey Ali ! kya farigh ho gaey ho?'' maine arz kiya : main uskey paas gaya tha magar us se khoon beh raha hai. aapney farmaya : ''usey chhod dey. yahan tak ke uska khoon ruk jaey. uskey baad usko had lagana aur apney ghulamon ko bhi had lagaya karo. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke ye hadees Abul Ahwas ne Abdul-A'alaa se aisey hi riwayat ki hai. aur Shoba ne Abdul-A'alaa se riwayat ki to us mein kaha : ''jab tak waza' hamal na ho jaey had na lagana .'' aur pehli riwayat ziyada sahih hai.
4474,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke jab meri baraa't (baree hone) ki aayaat nazil huin to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) member par khadey huey aur is waqiey ka zikr kiya aur Quran ki aayaat tilawat farmaeen . jab member se nichey utrey to aapney do mardon aur eik aurat ke mutalliq hukm diya aur unhen had lagai gaee.
4475,"Muhammad bin Is-haq ne ye riwayat bayan ki aur is mein Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ka zikr nahin kiya, bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do mardon aur eik aurat ko jo us tohmat mein shareek they, ke mutalliq (had laganey ka ( hukm diya. yani Hassaan bin Sabit aur Mistah bin Asaasa . Nufaili ne kaha ke aurton mein Hamna binte-Jahash ka zikr kartey hain."
4476,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sharab noshi ki had mutayyan nahin ki thi. ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain ke eik aadmi ne sharab pi li , us se usey nasha ho gaya aur gali mein laharaa laharaa kar chalney laga. phir usey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan ley chaley. jab wo Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar ke samney aaya to wo ghoom kar unke ghar mein chala gaya aur un se ja chimta . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye bataya gaya to aap hans padey aur puchha : ''kya waqae usney is tarah kiya hai?'' aur phir uskey baarey mein kuchh nahin farmaya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Hasan bin Ali ki is hadees ki riwayat mein ehale-Madina munfarid hain."
4477,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas eik aadmi laya gaya jisney sharab pi thi , to aapney farmaya : ''isey maaro.'' Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : ham mein se kisi ne usey haath se maara , kisi ne jootey se maara aur kisi ne kapdey se maara . jab wo aadmi wahan se chala to qom mein se kisi ne keh diya Allah tujhey ruswa karey. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''is tarah mat kaho. uskey khilaf shaitan ki madad mat karo.''"
4478,"Yahya bin Ayub , Hewa bin Shureh aur ibne Lahiya ne ibne Haad se iski sanad se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya. is riwayat mein maarney ke zikr ke baad yun hai ke phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Sahaba se farmaya : ''usey zara sharam dilao, tanbih karo.'' chunanche wo usey is tarah kehney lagey. tujhey Allah ka khof na aaya. tu Allah se dara nahin. tujhey Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se haya na aai. phir usko chhod diya aur riwayat ke aakhir mein hai. ''lekin yun kaho : aey Allah ! isko maaf kar dey. aey Allah ! is par rehem farma.'' aur baaz raawiyon ne isi qism ke alfaz ziyada bayan kiye hain."
4479,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sharab noshi ki had mein khajoor ki chhadiyon aur jooton se maara hai. aur Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne chaalis darrey (kodey) lagaey. jab Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) khalifa huey to unhoney Sahaba ko bulaya aur un se mashwara chaha ke log apney kheton aur zameenon mein chaley gaey hain. (yani jahan khajuren aur angoor waghaira ki farawani hai aur wo sharab peeney lagey hain). Musaddad ke alfaz mein hai ke log bastiyon aur zameenon mein chaley gaey hain. . . . to tum log sharab ki had ke baarey mein kya kehtey ho? to Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ham samajhtey hain ke aap isey sab se halki had ki manind kar den. chunanche unhoney is mein assi darrey (kodey) lagaey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ibne-Abi Aruba ne ba-waaste Qatada Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye hadees bayan ki ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khajoor ki chhadiyon aur jooton se chaalis zarbein lagaeen. jabkey Shoba ne Qatada se ba-waaste Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kiya to kaha ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khajoor ki do shaakhon se taqreeban chaalis zarbein lagaeen.
4480,"Huzain bin Munzir Raqashi Abu-Saasaan kehtey hain ke main Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan hazir tha ke Waleed bin Aqba ko laya gaya. to Humran aur eik doosrey aadmi ne us par gawahi di. eik ne kaha ke maine isko sharab peetey dekha hai aur doosrey ne kaha ke maine isko qai kartey dekha hai. to Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : isney sharab pi tabhi qai ki. phir Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke isko had lagao . Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke isko had lagao i. to Hazrat Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke iski haraarat usi ke hawaley keren jo uski thandak se lutf andoz hota hai. (ishara tha ke Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) hi ko ye kadwa kaseelaa kaam karna chahiye) phir Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abdullah bin Jaafar se kaha ke usko had lagao. to usney kudra liya aur maarney lagey aur Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) gintey jatey they. jab chaalis ko pahunchey to kaha ke bas, kafi hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne chaalis zarbein maari thin .(Huzain ne kaha) mera khayal hai ke yun kaha : Abu-Bakar ne chaalis aur umr ne assi zarbein maareen aur sab hi sunnat hai aur ye mujhey ziyada mehboob hai."
4481,"Huzain bin Munzir , Saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke sharab ki had mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur Saiyedna Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne chaalis zarbein maareen aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko assi  (80) se pura kiya, aur sab hi sunnat hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Ismaee ne ( ول حارها . . . . الخ (ka mafhoom ye bayan kiya ke is maamley ki sakhti aur shiddat usi ke supurd honi chahiye jo uski narmi aur rahat se mustafeed hota hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Huzain bin Munzir Abu-Saasaan apni qom ka sardar tha."
4482,"Saiyedna Muawiya bin Abu-Sufiyaan (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(shraabi) jab sharab piyen to unhen darrey lagao , phir agar piyen to darrey lagao , phir agar piyen to darrey lagao phir agar piyen to qatl kar do.''"
4483,Janab Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya. . . . aur mazkura baala ke ham-maani riwayat kiya. unhoney kaha : mera khayal hai ke paanchwin baar aapney farmaya : ''agar piye to usey qatl kar do. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Abu-Ghutaif ki riwayat mein bhi paanchwin baar ka zikr hai.
4484,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab wo nashay se mast ho to usey darrey lagao , phir agar mast ho to darrey lagao , phir agar mast ho to darrey lagao , agar chauthi baar dohraaey, to usey qatl kar do . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke umr bin Abi Salma ki riwayat mein bhi aisey hi hai jo wo apney walid sey, wo Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se aur wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain : ''jab wo sharab piye to usey kodey lagao agar chauthi baar piye to usey qatl kar do. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke : ( Suhel bin Abi Saleh Abi Huraira Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( ki sanad se bhi yehi marwi (bayan) hai : ''agar chauthi baar peiyen to unhen qatl kar do. aisey hi ibne-Abi Nu'am ki riwayat mein hai jo ba-waaste ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se naqal hui hai. isi tarah Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) aur Shareed ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kiya hai. aur Jadli (Abd bin Abd) ki riwayat jo ba-waaste Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se manqul hai us mein hai : ''agar teesri ya chauthi baar piye to usey qatl kar do.''"
4485,"Saiyedna Qabisa bin Zuwaib (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo sharab piye to usey kodey lagao, agar phir piye to kodey lagao , agar phir teesri ya chauthi baar piye to usey qatl kar do.'' phir aap ke paas eik aadmi laya gaya jisney sharab pi thi to aapney usey kodey lagaey. phir dobara laya gaya to kodey lagaey, phir laya gaya to kodey lagaey, phir laya gaya to kodey lagaey aur qatl chhod diya to is tarah qatl se rukhsat mil gaee. Sufiyan kehtey hain ke Zohri ne ye riwayat us waqt bayan ki jab Mansoor bin Motamir aur Mukhawwal bin Rashid unke paas baithey they. Zohri ne un se kaha ke ehale-Iraq ke paas ye hadees tohfa ley jana. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is riwayat ko Shareed bin Suwaid, Shurehbil bin Aus , Abdullah bin Amr , Abdullah bin umr , Abu-Ghutaif Kandi aur Abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman ne Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ke wastey se naqal kiya hai."
4486,Ameerul-momeneen Saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main kisi par had qaaim karun (aur wo mar jaey) to kisi ki diyat na dun siwaye sharab peene wale ke. bila-shuba Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us mein koi had mutayyan nahin farmaee thi. ye had ham ne (mashwarey sey) tey ki hai.
4487,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Azhar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain goya ke main ab bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekh raha hun, aap paalaanon mein khadey Hazrat Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ka paalaan talash kar rahey they ke achcha aap ke paas eik aadmi laya gaya jisney sharab pi rakhi thi. aapney logon se kaha : ''isko maaro.'' chunanche baaz ne usko jooton se maara , baaz ne lathi se aur baaz ne (ميتخة) se. ibne-Wahab ne wazahat ki ke is se murad khajoor ki tar-o-taza chhadi hai. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne zameen se kuch mitti li aur uskey munh par maari."
4488,"Janab Abdullah bin Abdur-Rehman bin Azhar apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas eik shraabi laya gaya jabkey aap Hunain mein they to aapney uskey munh par mitti maari. phir aapney apney Sahaba se farmaya to unhoney usko jooton se aur jo unke haath mein tha us se maara , yahan tak ke aapney farmaya : ''bas karo.''  to wo ruk gaey. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat ho gaee to Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne sharab peeney par chaalis zarbein lagaeen. phir Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi apney ibtidaai (shuruati) daur mein chaalis zarbein hi lagaeen aur aakhiri daur mein assi (80) laganey lagey . phir Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne dono tarah amal kiya, assi bhi aur chaalis bhi . phir Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye had assi (80) kodon par pukhta kar di."
4489,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Azhar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Fateh Makka ki subah ko dekha, main us moqe par khoob jawan tha, aap logon ke darmiyan mein se ja rahey they aur Hazrat Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ka padaaw daryaft farma rahey they ke eik shraabi aap ke paas laya gaya. to aapney logon ko hukm diya to unhoney usko jo unke haath mein tha, maara . baaz ne kudra maara , baaz ne lathi maari , baaz ne apna joota maara aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us par mitti phenki. phir jab Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka daur aaya to eik sharab peene wala laya gaya , to unhoney Sahaba se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka amal daryaft farmaya ke unhoney kis qadr maara tha. to unhoney uska andaza chaalis zarbon ka lagaya . chunanche Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne chaalis zarbein lagaeen. phir jab Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka daur aaya to Hazrat Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko likha ke log sharab peeney mein munhamik ho gaey hain aur is had aur saza ko wo maamuli samajhtey hain. unhoney kaha : Sahaba kiram aap ke paas hain un se daryaft keejiye. aur aap ke paas daure-awwal ke Muhajir Sahaba mojud they, to aapney un se mashwara kiya. unhoney ittifaq kiya ke aisey logon ko assi (80) zarbein lagai jaeyn. Saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : tehqiq shraabi jab sharab peeta hai to jhoot boltaa aur tohmat lagata hai, so main samajhta hun ke is had ko tohmat ki had ki manind kar diya jaey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Aqeel bin Khalid ne is riwayat ki sanad mein Zohri aur Abdur-Rehman bin Azhar ke beech Abdullah bin Abdur-Rehman bin Azhar an Abih ka izafa kar diya hai."
4490,"Hazrat Hakim bin Hizam (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne masjid mein qisaas leney , ashaar padhney aur haden laganey se mana farmaya hai."
4491,"Hazrat Abu-Barda (Haani bin Dinar Ansari (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : ''Allah ki mutaiyena hudood ke alawa kisi jurm mein das kodon se ziyada na maarey jaeyn.''"
4492,"Hazrat Abu-Barda Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna . . . . aur mazkura baala riwayat ke ham-maani bayan kiya."
4493,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi shakhs maarey to chehrey par na maarey.''"
